{
  "stem": "22883.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I could-- the whole problem treated differently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Not be that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] indifferent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that was the-- the-- my reaction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My-- I-- I-- actually, you know, in life, many things, they happen spontaneous.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there was not much of reasoning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because if I would reason, if I would think about, I would never get into this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This is extremely dangerous situation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's incredibly dangerous situation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But somehow, I felt that I have to-- to make up for that indifference of my people and even my family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that's the-- the answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the liberation, we were still in the same-- well, not the same place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this camp where we were put by this company [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was anyway, we did work at that time because it was Eastern holiday.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, of course, everything was falling apart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no-- no-- no work, and there was no decent work, because the-- the Russians were coming, OK?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] in this camp, there was a-- one Frenchman, older, a little bit older than me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was Italian origin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was-- at that time, he knew a lady who had the house on the other side of-- there was such a-- a-- not a street, but rail-- not-- [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] would be highway, which was not finished.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was not finished highway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And beyond that highway, there were small houses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So from the camp, you could see only chimneys of these houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- one of the ladies, owner of such a small house, asked him to come for the front coming to-- just to be in the house and to take care of the house.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
